link:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>因此结论成立。</p><p>定理2.6：设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为随机矩阵，若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18153-formula24"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x76_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>证明：令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则有</p><p><img src="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x83_hanspub.png" />,<img src="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x84_hanspub.png" /> (2.4)</p><p>于是</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.18153-formula25"><label>(2.5)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x85_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.18153-formula26"><label>(2.6)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x86_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/8-1250457x